The signzone tool is part of the OpenDNSSEC project.
For more information, visit http://www.opendnssec.org

CONTENTS:
    INTRODUCTION
    DEPENDENCIES
    INSTALLATION
    INTERACTION FROM THE COMMAND LINE

-------------------------------------------------------------------
INTRODUCTION
-------------------------------------------------------------------

As part of the OpenDNSSEC project, this tool signs zones in
a {ldns,dnssec}-signzone way.

-------------------------------------------------------------------
DEPENDENCIES
-------------------------------------------------------------------

The signzone tool depends on the ldns library:

	 http://www.NLnetLabs.nl/projects/ldns

and can only be used in conjuction with a PKCS#11 library (a software
version of which, softHSM, is supplied with the OpenDNSSEC).

-------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALLATION
-------------------------------------------------------------------

The signzone tool is installed as part of the OpenDNSSEC install.

-------------------------------------------------------------------
INTERACTION FROM THE COMMAND LINE
-------------------------------------------------------------------

The following commands are supported:

sign		sign a zone.
roll		roll keys for a zone.

